General.Name: Aumake Ltd
General.Description: AuMake Limited engages in the sale of Australian products through its online e-commerce store and retail stores. It offers beverages and alcohol; food products, including dairy, Fresh fruits, seafood, honey, wine, beef, mutton, and lamb; and health and beauty products, such as vitamins, protein shakes/meal replacement shakes, supplements, and herbs/herbal teas. It also provides fashion, homewares, art and craft, metal work, and leatherwear; and health and wellbeing products, such as vitamins, nutritional supplements, mineral supplements, non-prescription medicines, and drugs made in Australian and New Zealand laboratories. In addition, it also provides international importing, exporting, and warehousing services. AuMake Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Parramatta, Australia.
